column2: SELECT spec.bestobjid, spec.ra, spec.dec, spec.z, spec.class,   phot.fiberMag_u as u_aper, phot.extinction_u as u_aper_ext,   phot.fiberMag_g as g_aper, phot.extinction_g as g_aper_ext,   phot.fiberMag_r as r_aper, phot.extinction_r as r_aper_ext,   phot.fiberMag_i as i_aper, phot.extinction_i as i_aper_ext,   phot.fiberMag_z as z_aper, phot.extinction_z as z_aper_ext INTO MyDB.DR1#_S8#_Spec_Galaxies_# FROM SpecObj as spec, PhotoObj as phot WHERE spec.BestObjID = phot.ObjID AND (   spec.class = &&& AND (spec.zWarning = # OR spec.zWarning = #) AND spec.ra BETWEEN # and # AND spec.dec BETWEEN # and # )
